{"tid":808941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底咁樣影相有咩意義？","createTime":"2018-09-06T17:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T17:40:47.000Z","uid":200739,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1911c6150067dc65306fe1d52015f7a282b7f8","tid":808941,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:30:51.000Z","msg":"仲記得以前細細個小學嗰陣，聖誕嗰陣大家都會帶晒啲零食/屋企自己整嘅嘢食返去聯歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家食下嘢吹下水幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但到左近年手機一出現啲活動就即刻變撚晒質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下下係又影唔係又影，嗰啲陸運會/水運會/聖誕party/last day/畢業禮/旅行 全撚部變晒做影相環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實到底咁樣集郵有啲咩意義，你同晒百幾二百人影相，又影晒啲團體照，但你跟本就無享受過嗰個活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住就係ig到打埋晒啲咩最後一次旅行乜乜柒柒，每次活動都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要大部份影完嘅相一po完上ig snapchat就唔會再攞出嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但就扮到好撚有回憶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成件事真係好撚on9<br />\n<br />\n好掛住以前大家一齊享受活動嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4beaa81e24874723eb9176567d737f16218f7c6f","tid":808941,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係咁"},{"pid":"4b5ce3306afe00dea678e4bc57a778135550c1da","tid":808941,"uid":207426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5abc0a4bcbe0e1aeed8e6268fb71cd72d0a955b","tid":808941,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"仲記得前一年中學christmas party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全班無人帶嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住6個鐘全程啲人去晒其他班9影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個班房空晒無人"},{"pid":"2dc2ad56e2fa8edf494051b05a681a6fa435d94a","tid":808941,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4beaa81e24874723eb9176567d737f16218f7c6f","tid":808941,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:36:20.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a80cf305ea4c9beb931f295a8a614313138cd40","tid":808941,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5ce3306afe00dea678e4bc57a778135550c1da","tid":808941,"uid":207426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"如果係一班影一兩張班相其實ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cls啲人係會逐個逐個全級嘅人都要影一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔明有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n最後啲相我睇都無睇過就save晒入google drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea8442e26ecdde2f6fbb38c38f07e0057c00b79","tid":808941,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a80cf305ea4c9beb931f295a8a614313138cd40","tid":808941,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5ce3306afe00dea678e4bc57a778135550c1da","tid":808941,"uid":207426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"如果係一班影一兩張班相其實ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cls啲人係會逐個逐個全級嘅人都要影一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔明有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n最後啲相我睇都無睇過就save晒入google drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"因為係帶團個個做portfolio record唔係比你"}]}